    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3244350/extras/6f05c7709bda1187826ed4c779a768da.poster.avif?t=1756344479\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3244350/extras/6f05c7709bda1187826ed4c779a768da.webm?t=1756344479\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3244350/extras/6f05c7709bda1187826ed4c779a768da.mp4?t=1756344479\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《草莓蛋糕的埋葬》拥有<strong>无法预测的故事</strong>。本作的角色设计由声优・佐佐木望（Sasaki Nozomi）担任，她拥有的表演经历让角色绽放出特殊的“<strong>表情冲击力</strong>”，本作就是具有如此特点的新颖视觉小说。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >点击画面，推进故事发展。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏特征</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3244350/extras/02e2dd88827a6d6a6d5362fea21644a3.poster.avif?t=1756344479\" width=494 height=278 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3244350/extras/02e2dd88827a6d6a6d5362fea21644a3.webm?t=1756344479\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3244350/extras/02e2dd88827a6d6a6d5362fea21644a3.mp4?t=1756344479\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >・类别：犯罪悬疑・视觉小说</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >・游戏时长：5小时~7小时左右</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >・无选项</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >故事</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >“汗液，土壤，血液，如上种种。一旦全都侵入口中， 就立刻想吐。”</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >潜入深夜山林，因某事而不得不埋葬遗体的主人公・季节。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >铲雪用的铁锹。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >超市的手推车。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >然后，用蓝色篷布包裹隐藏起的——“那个”。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >以上种种，包围着季节。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >他擦去汗水，饮下血与土，挖掘着地洞。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >然后，他终于意识到。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >“……哈？”</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >意识到，在地洞的彼方，在悲剧的彼方没有尽头。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >描绘着悲剧的，在那之后的彼端的正是——</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >犯罪悬疑视觉小说——《草莓蛋糕的埋葬》</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >制作成员</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >企划・剧本・演出・动画　齋藤瑠久 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >角色设计 ささきのぞみ（Sasaki Nozomi） </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >音乐 上久保汐李 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >静态插图 ささきのぞみ（Sasaki Nozomi）　おのやま（Ono Yama）　アヤベエリコ（Ayabe Eriko）</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >中文翻译 ≠悠</p>",
